        "eyebrow": "The Re-Manifesto",
        "heading": "Every product has a next chapter. We intend to be part of it.",
        "body": "<p>Most things are made to be replaced. We make things to be kept.<br/>Keeping isn’t just about durability — it’s about what happens years later, as homes and lives change. At narkk, a product’s story doesn’t end at the sale.<br/>We take responsibility for the full arc — through five commitments.</p>"
